{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "百物語", "storyInfo": "森內、萌萌香和“神明”意識到御機的怪談絕大多數其實都是三船的設計，感到強烈的幻滅。但他們還來不及想接下來的事，三船派出的忍者就殺了過來，擄走了森內。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g11_odenstall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electricbicycle_speedup", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊小姐，還有萌萌香？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先吃點東西墊一下肚子？還是說我拜託兩位的事情這麼快就有結果了？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃、吃東西就不用了……一路騎到這裡，我覺得自己喝了好多風……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金石會的人還在追你們？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧神明大人的指點，再加上我們特地挑了人跡罕至的路線，回來的路還算順利。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明大人……難道說？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別高興的太早。雖然的確是神明大人，但並不是你要找的那位。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒關係，沒關係！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monocycle_bell"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的沒關係？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您、您是……？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們看，我就說嘛。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "森內", "content": "不，不不！小店沒有什麼能招待您的，您看要不要……來點關東煮湯暖暖身體——"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "森內", "content": "不對，所有的關東煮都隨便您挑！"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不像某些傢伙，那麼執著你的關東煮。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明大人，不知您——", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知什麼？不知我有沒有見過你口中的招財貓，對不對？你要找的根本就不是我，而是他。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不敢！能見到一位神明，對我來說已經是天大的喜事，我怎麼敢挑剔呢？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你的眼睛明明就不是這樣說的。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我和那個傢伙還能聊得上天的時候，他口中的你才沒有這麼做作。你那時候還只是一個小孩子，小孩子怎麼對待朋友，你就怎麼對待他。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……祂就是因為這個離我而去的嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我哪知道。他記得你，但你也不過是他打過交道的無數人中的一個。他才不會費心地告訴我為什麼“離你而去”。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來找你有別的理由。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題！您想從我這裡得到什麼？金錢？還是情報？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$formal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然是情報。有關怪談的情報。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為御機的怪談都是我們這樣的神明做的，但我可以明確告訴你，基本上全都不是。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不正是怪談“輪入道”的本體嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不否認自己每天騎著獨輪車朝氣蓬勃地在街上跑，但除此之外呢？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都廳街的那個警察署背後的舊樓。“不存在的電梯”。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有十五層的大樓裡竟然有顯示十六層的按鈕，多出來的一層便是“地獄”，那裡發生過失蹤事件。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且櫃台的招財貓裝飾品和十六層出現的時機息息相關。那個固定在檯面上的招財貓偶爾會消失，第二天又重新出現在檯面上。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的事情不僅發生在那棟舊樓，還有很多人都跟我說過類似的事情，“招財貓飾品莫名其妙不見又出現”之類的。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體到那棟舊樓，每次“誤入地獄”事件發生的時候，招財貓的裝飾品都不見了。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#2$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道得很詳細嘛，但我偏偏能夠確定，那棟大樓的招財貓裝飾品和你想找的“神明”，除了長得像之外，沒有任何關係。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問您有什麼證據嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還需要證據嗎？我就是神明，分辨一樣東西和神明有沒有關係，輕而易舉。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只能算空口無憑——", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才那副恭順的樣子呢？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是想責難你。像現在這樣有什麼說什麼，比剛才那樣好多了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，我也是仔仔細細探查過那棟舊樓的。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一，那根本就不是什麼隱藏按鈕。十六層的按鈕是嵌在十五層按鈕上面的，被鋼板擋住了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那肯定不是神明做的，你們人類也不可能掀動那個東西。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十六層的按鈕一直都在那裡……只是被鋼板擋住了？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內的臉色忽然變得有些難看。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看吧，你也覺得自己有點笨，對不對？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二，那個招財貓是按得動的。用力按，按下去，能把整個裝飾品按到檯面下。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您……按了？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按了啊，按了之後也沒發生什麼事。櫃台人員回來的時候隨便弄一下，那個裝飾品就又冒出來了。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後那個櫃台人員就開始接電話，接了一長串，一直在道歉什麼的。就這樣。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看吧，你只是把真正的怪談和那個櫃台的怪癖聯想在一起而已。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……怎麼可能是怪癖呢？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#9$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然還能是什麼？把招財貓裝飾品壓到櫃台的檯面裡，難道是他和你剛好相反，跟那個傢伙有什麼仇怨？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小妹妹，怎麼了？你去那裡拍攝過節目？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，但之前綜藝節目取材的時候，一個同事曾經提過這個點子，然後被事務所所長罵了一頓。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罵了一頓？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所長說了很多我聽不太懂的話，說是裡面有個“鐵火場”是金石會的產業什麼的。大概是飯館，怕拍攝節目影響生意吧。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵火場？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵火場？！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，怎麼了？“鐵火”是一種鱗獸料理的名字，那鐵火場不就是賣鐵火的飯館嗎？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……“鐵火場”是賭場的暗語。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來“地獄”只是金石會的賭場，有人誤入那裡後被封口了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十六層的按鈕得透過某種機關才會出現，多半對應的是某個夾層，或者是地下室。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個招財貓裝飾品大概是發信裝置，按下去就會發出通知，所以“神明大人”按了之後才會有人打電話，那個櫃台人員才會道歉。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香感嘆了一聲，不知是為森內感到惋惜，還是得知怪談並非超自然力量後鬆了口氣。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好事的神明略微有些煩躁地用爪子抓抓頭，顯然沒料到怪談竟然如此收場。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而森內的臉色越來越青，越來越青，直到汗水都從他的額頭上流了下來。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一定只是巧合……只是巧合。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年了，也有怪談被證明是以訛傳訛的，但總有那麼多怪談沒有人能解釋！十六層的地獄只是個巧合！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有“尚存於世的福井家食堂”，我以前和那位神明大人還有來往的時候，祂曾經告訴過我，祂蠻喜歡那家店的。", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩年前那家店被拆了以後，偶爾有人說附近能聞到炸物的香氣，還有人說，那塊空地上有時還能看見店面，只是不能走近——", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡被拆了之後一直都是空地啊。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那家店我有印象。當時我想去探店，店主不讓我進去，我就去了另一家。那期節目播出之後沒過多久，店就倒了。", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幾天到處都在傳，說是我詛咒了那家店，不然就是“怪談女王又發威了”，還有“這是報復吧！這個人根本就是睚眦必報”之類的話……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那家店就是金石會拆的啊。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道！但我們說的是拆掉之後的事！萌萌香，那家店拆掉以後，你們節目組不是還去過一次嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#5$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對、對啊，但是……那次我也就只聞到了炸物的香氣，其實沒看到店面……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想讓人聞到某種香氣很簡單的吧。假如完全不考慮怪談，這件事不就是金石會想要強拆福井家食堂嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先給人留下一種這裡可能發生怪談的印象，然後強拆，最後再派萌萌香去一次。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……那……青鬼的……兇宅！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……森內老闆，你要在我前面聊這個嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思冒犯了，但那間兇宅的人既然不是你害的，那就仍然有可能是神明！", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連這位神明大人，不也是在兇宅的怪談傳開之後才開始追逐怪談的嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確是這樣沒錯。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香，你最近不是還去過那間兇宅拍攝節目了嗎？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#19$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈……啊哈哈……雖然我不是被幽靈嚇到，是被星熊嚇到就是了。我當時還抓起地上的東西想打她——", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#19$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“別忘了，滿屋的垃圾，她偏偏撿起了那把斷刀，當時我們怎麼找都找不到，只能草草偽造了一把的斷刀。”"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“就算她是無心的，事情的性質也已經變了。”"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不不不……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘴上說著否定的話，但萌萌香仍然顫抖著手，從懷中拿出了那柄斷刀。"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊，這、這只是一把斷刀，對不對？三船先生不會因為這個東西就想滅我的口的，對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斷刀？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拍節目那天在你家撿到的，昨晚半夜我家電視故障的時候，我好像聽見三船先生說，說因為我撿了這把刀……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看這個刀鐔，這不是佐野口那把家傳寶刀嗎？他當年很喜歡向其他人炫耀的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佐野口？兇宅的第二個受害者，用家傳寶刀砍死妻子然後自盡的人？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是不只一個警察告訴我，他的刀已經鎖在警察的證物室裡面了，怎麼會放在你家老宅裡呢？", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#11$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定是三船先生貪圖這把刀，交了假的證物上去對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這把刀怎麼不在他的收藏裡，反而放在我家，甚至還只剩半截？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，發瘋自盡這種事，黑道簡直是歡迎警察來查兇手，就為了看警察什麼都查不到，恨恨離去的樣子……沒有道理還偽造證物。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非佐野口不是自盡，是金兵衛……", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……殺了他。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香愣住了。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊接著，彷彿從夢中醒來，卻只是進入了另一個惡夢一樣，她甚至比森內還要呆滯地看著星熊。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在開玩笑，對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些怪談……那些把我嚇得要死的怪談……怎麼可能不是真的？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事務所再怎麼不像話，也不可能……這麼多年一直製造……各種……各樣的……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那位佐野口，只有他的……他的死……有問題，而其他人……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#20$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的聲音越來越低，直到徹底消失。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她下意識地望向森內，森內卻故意移開了視線。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她忽然意識到，自己看森內是覺得森內和自己同病相憐，而森內移開視線是因為他不願意承認這一點。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以那些被我探訪過之後關閉的店……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些我明明按照指示做了，卻還是出了錯，結果有人受傷的直播……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些怪聲、幽靈、飄忽的怪影，都是……假的？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連我深信不疑，這幾天把我嚇得魂飛魄散的青鬼和兇宅的怪談，御機所有怪談的起點，其實也是……假的？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羽生萌萌香，怪談纏身的藝人，我的職業生涯對事務所來說……其實不重要？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我在他們眼裡只是一個……用來掩護金石會的……擋箭牌？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內老闆，這肯定只是我們想多了，對不對？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "森內"}, "figure_art": "avg_4199_makiri_1#4$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 6.0, "times": 40.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-100", "duration": 0.6, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內老闆……？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$prisonbreak_intro", "key": "$prisonbreak_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敵襲！躲到我後面！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香仍然愣在原地，星熊跨上一步，用般若護在她和倒在地上的森內身前。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hiddenweapon_hitshield"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_USB_explode", "channel": "a", "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿要給萌萌香剛才的疑問一個回答似的，盾面上傳來密密麻麻的輕微爆炸聲。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明大人，麻煩你看看森內到底是怎麼了，是中毒了還是被什麼東西打中了？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1904_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內的脖子上有個焦痕，旁邊掉著這個東西。", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是你們拿來在終端間傳輸資訊的隨身碟嗎？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前倒是也見過有人丟這個東西癱瘓別人的電子設備，最近怎麼都開始往別人身上丟了？", "name": "好事的神明"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,100", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忍者？！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#18$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要抵抗。", "name": "沉默的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰派你來的？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不重要。跟我走。", "name": "沉默的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定不是三船先生派你來的，是不是？", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這個問題，我還是第一次聽人這麼問。", "name": "沉默的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，怪談都是真的！我的職業生涯不是三船……不是金兵衛的擋箭牌！", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忍者不答，只是亮出了手中似刀非刀的兵器，儘管還未刺出，卻已經直指星熊的前胸。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一輩子生活在陰影中，從不以真面目招搖過市的間諜、陰謀家、縱火犯，乃至暗殺者。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從數百年前國戰戕亂時起，這些人就開始以忍者之名潛伏在歷史的陰影中。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，大名、公卿、財閥、首領……無數有權有勢的人豢養過類似的組織。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1", "duration": 0.4, "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "-200,0"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 1.0, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "jump", "posto": "500,0", "power": 100.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 60.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚？！", "name": "偷襲的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藏得不錯，但出手太慢了。", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "duration": 0.3, "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "540,160", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_branchrupture"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_USB_explode", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.5, "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊一腳踩在剛剛被自己擋下的隨身碟上，隨身碟先是吱吱作響，然後砰的一聲爆開。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還蠻跟得上時代的嘛，具有高壓電的隨身碟。人機兩用？", "name": "星熊"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個忍者對視一眼，短刀、太刀，二人一左一右，直撲萌萌香而去。"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死纏爛打！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 2.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing5", "channel": "2", "delay": 0.05}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing6", "channel": "3", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "般若在星熊手裡旋轉成耀眼的圓形，太刀在外層的刃上捲得粉碎，而持短刀的忍者不得不撲倒在地，免得連手臂都在其中絞斷。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到這時，一直藏在陰影中的第三人才露出身形，數枚隨身碟不發出一點聲音，直撲星熊的後腦。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再出聲提醒已經來不及了，於是萌萌香一躍而起，想學著電影裡的樣子用背包把那些小東西打回去……"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_handknf"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果自己被打個正著。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shockbody"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 0.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "細小的劈啪聲響過，她連哼都沒哼一聲，和森內一樣跌落在地上，軟成一團。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖！", "name": "伺機的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只剩你一個了。要嘛乖乖跟我們走，要嘛像他們一樣倒下。結局都一樣。", "name": "沉默的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼自信不是一件好事。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……廢話少說，動手。", "name": "伺機的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 1.0, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hiddenweapon_hitshield"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "afrom": 1.0, "rfrom": 1.0, "gfrom": 1.0, "bfrom": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hiddenweapon_hitshield", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hiddenweapon_hitshield", "channel": "2", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hiddenweapon_hitshield", "channel": "3", "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暗器從能想到的方向打來，從想不到的方向打來，卻全數在舞動的般若上撞得粉碎。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想背著兩個人一起跑！攔住她！", "name": "伺機的忍者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch_xshield"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "channel": "n"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊朝著最近的忍者猛衝，穿著黑衣的刺客直接撞在盾面上，也不知斷了幾根肋骨。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她本打算就這麼突破包圍，肩上忽然一輕，森內被什麼東西拖上了半空。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鉤爪？！", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內還在空中，萌萌香也像抓娃娃機裡的玩偶一樣被鉤了起來——"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wiatear_break", "delay": 0.5, "channel": "m"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "般若將連著鉤爪的繩索切斷，萌萌香掉回星熊懷中，關東煮攤老闆卻被慣性丟在了自己的攤子前面。"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "channel": "z"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知哪個忍者抓起老闆一躍而起，消失在仁田街的樓與樓之間。"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星、星熊……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你醒得很快。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我脖子好痛……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是被電流燒的。好好照顧，應該不會留疤。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鍛冶町的方向似乎還有伏兵，你有別的地方可以讓我們暫時躲一下嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我家。但金兵衛應該已經派人去過了……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越危險的地方反而越安全，他們不一定能猜到我們會去那裡。再說，就算真的有人在，我們換一個地方就好了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那太好了，這樣我還可以帶葉助一起……", "name": "萌萌香"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1918_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葉助？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，有時間再解釋。越拖人就越多。你家在哪個方向？我們現在就過去。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明大人，你——", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#2$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……已經不見了啊。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_136_hsguma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}